      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We headed under the bridge, towards a fountain in the center of the park.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['07/IMG_2239','07/DSC03083','07/IMG_2246'], right: ['07/DSC03082','07/DSC03137'] })
