    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          After taking in the park for a little while, we decided to whittle away the early afternoon at Fort Pitt Museum.

    = partial("photoessays/components/place_of_interest", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '07/DSC03143', title: 'Fort Pitt Museum', address: '601 Commonwealth Pl, Pittsburgh, PA 15222, USA', place: 'Museum', rating: 5, link:'' })
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['07/IMG_2351'], right: ['07/IMG_2369'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          The museum was surprisingly large, with plenty of historic artwork and recreated scenes. Our tourguide was very knowledgeable and walked us through the various display, giving us a rich account of the history of Pittsburgh and Fort Pitt.

          ---

          It was now early afternoon, so we decided to head back towards our hotel and check in.

          One train ride, and a walk through the south end of the city later, we arrived.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '07/IMG_2373'})
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '07/DSC03204'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          That evening, after we’d packed and had a quick rest in our rooms, we headed out in search of dinner.

          We couldn’t all decide what to get for dinner as a group. So in the end, Irwin, Butcher, and I opted for a Middle Eastern place on E Carlson st.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/place_restaurant", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '07/kassab', title: 'Kassab’s Restaurant', address: '1207 E Carson St, Pittsburgh, PA 15203, USA', price: '$', menu: 'Middle Eastern', rating: 5, link: '' })
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['07/IMG_3514'], right: ['07/IMG_3512'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          The food here was delicious; the lamb gyro was incredibly full of flavour.

          After a very filling meal, we met up with the others at a nearby bar.
    
    = partial("photoessays/components/place_drink", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '07/jacks-bar', title: 'Jack’s Bar', address: '1117 E Carson St, Pittsburgh, PA 15203, USA', price: '$', menu: 'Bar', rating: 5, link: '' })
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['07/IMG_3519','07/IMG_3521'], right: ['07/IMG_3520','07/IMG_3527'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We particularly enjoyed the Blue Moon and Summer Shandy beers.

          Many drinks later, we returned back to the hotel for bed.

    .Row#august-08
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          ---

          The next morning, I awoke quite early, and headed for the breakfast buffet.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_right", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '08/IMG_3529'})

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          It was starting to get a little late in the morning now, and the others were still resting. Approaching 11am and feeling a bit bored of waiting, I decided to head out by myself and explore E Carlson street again.   

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_full", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, caption: '', photo: '08/IMG_3532'})
