    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          I continued down E Carson street, noticing a shop I thought the rest of the crew would like to check out; a game exchange shop.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['08/IMG_3543'], right: ['08/IMG_3542'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          By now, the rest of the group were up, so I headed back to the hotel to meet up with them.

          We headed back down E Carson street, and headed in to the 

    = partial("photoessays/components/place_of_interest", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '08/exchange-southside-pittsburg', title: 'The Exchange', address: '1709 E Carson St, Pittsburgh, PA 15203, USA', place: 'Trade in store', rating: 5, link:'' })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          Inside was a wide variety of second hand music, media, videogames, and more miscellaneous paraphenalia.

          We spent a long time searching up and down the various ailses.

    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['08/IMG_3546','08/IMG_3548'], right: ['08/IMG_3547','08/IMG_3550','08/IMG_3551'] })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We spoke to one of the people behind the register. She was surprised to see people from overseas traveling through Pittsburgh — it kind of was a self-deprecating tone that felt familiar as native Perth folks.
          
          After a good look around, it was time to get some lunch.

    = partial("photoessays/components/place_restaurant", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, image: '08/fatheads', title: 'Fat Head’s Saloon', address: ' 1805 E Carson St, Pittsburgh, PA 15203, USA', price: '$$', menu: 'Beer and Burger', rating: 5, link: '' })

    .Row
      .Content_Main.Content_Article
        :markdown
          We ended up at Fatheads, which paired craft beers with some very excellent burgers.
          
    = partial("photoessays/components/photo_two_column", locals: {slug: current_page.data.slug, left: ['08/IMG_3552','08/IMG_3556','08/IMG_3559','08/IMG_3564'], right: ['08/IMG_4361','08/IMG_3554','08/IMG_3558'] })
